      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：噬膚滅鼻，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows one biting through the soft flesh, and (going on to) bite off the nose. There will be no error.</seg>
