      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：噬臘肉，遇毒；小吝，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows one gnawing dried flesh, and meeting with what is disagreeable. There will be occasion for some small regret, but no (great) error.</seg>
