      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：噬乾胏，得金矢，利艱貞，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows one gnawing the flesh dried on the bone, and getting the pledges of money and arrows. It will be advantageous to him to realise the difficulty of his task and be firm,--in which case there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
